KLUPONK (04/13/2026)

Player play 3 rounds.

Cupboy Phase: Cupboy is determined by shotgun contest fastest shotgun wins. Players must hold their empty drink above their head to
show they have finished! Winning player is Cupboy. Players may decide if they want to compete in the Cupboy Phase. 

Cupboy then places a solo cup in a spot of their choosing. Cupboy the decides the starting point and places a marker.

Each player takes a playing card(1-3), the player then may take that many steps.

The Goal is to make a shot into the solo cup using a ping-pong ball. Everyshot a player makes is 1 point.

If a player moans before taking their shot and make it, then every other player has to take a shot. If they miss the player takes 2 shots.

Players can gamble their points on another players shot. If the player gambles correctly they double their wagered points, if they fail they loose the wagered points.

Winner is the player who makes the most shots!

